      caption: "\u{1F537} REFERRAL NETWORK\n\u2726 Share Your Link, Earn From 20 Levels \u2014 Unlimited Width\n\nTurboLoop's referral network transforms every member into a potential income hub. Share your unique referral link, and when someone joins and deposits through it, you earn a percentage of their deposit \u2014 automatically, daily, processed by the smart contract. But it doesn't stop at direct referrals. TurboLoop's network extends 20 levels deep, meaning you earn from your referrals' referrals' referrals \u2014 all the way down to the 20th level. The total distribution across all levels is 51%, with no limit on width at any level. You can refer 10 people or 10,000 \u2014 the smart contract tracks and distributes commissions for every single one, every single day, without fail.\n\n\u2705 Key Highlights:\n\u2022 20 levels deep \u2014 earn from your entire network's activity\n\u2022 51% total distribution across all 20 referral levels\n\u2022 Unlimited width \u2014 no cap on referrals at any level\n\u2022 Automatic daily payments processed by smart contract\n\u2022 Your unique referral link = your passive income engine\n\n\u{1F48E} One link. Twenty levels. Unlimited potential. Start sharing.\n\n\u{1F310} turboloop.io",
