      caption: "\u{1F537} THE POWER OF COMPOUNDING\n\u2726 Einstein's Eighth Wonder \u2014 Applied to DeFi Yield\n\nAlbert Einstein reportedly called compound interest 'the eighth wonder of the world,' and TurboLoop makes this wonder accessible to everyone. The principle is simple: instead of withdrawing your returns at the end of each cycle, reinvest them into a new plan. Your next cycle earns returns on a larger base, which produces even larger returns, which compound again. Using Power Loop (24%/30 days) as an example: $1,000 becomes $1,240 after Month 1. Reinvested, it grows to $1,907 by Month 3, $3,654 by Month 6, $7,003 by Month 9, and a remarkable $13,220 by Month 12. That's over 1,200% growth in one year from a single initial deposit. The smart contract doesn't know or care about your compounding strategy \u2014 it simply calculates returns on whatever amount you deposit, with mathematical precision.\n\n\u2705 Key Highlights:\n\u2022 $1,000 \u2192 $1,240 (Month 1) \u2192 $1,907 (Month 3)\n\u2022 $3,654 (Month 6) \u2192 $7,003 (Month 9) \u2192 $13,220 (Month 12)\n\u2022 Over 1,200% growth in 12 months through disciplined reinvestment\n\u2022 Works with any deposit amount \u2014 the math scales proportionally\n\u2022 Smart contract calculates with identical precision every cycle\n\n\u{1F48E} Time multiplies your money. Start compounding today.\n\n\u{1F310} turboloop.io",
