      caption: "\u{1F537} REFERRAL NETWORK \u2014 DETAILED\n\u2726 The Complete Architecture of 20-Level Earnings\n\nTurboLoop's referral network is a 20-level deep, unlimited-width earning structure that distributes 51% of referred deposits to network builders. Here's the complete architecture: Your unique referral link is generated automatically when you connect your wallet. When someone joins through your link and deposits, you earn Level 1 commission (12%) on their deposit. When they refer someone, you earn Level 2 (8%). This cascades through all 20 levels: L3 (5%), L4-5 (3% each), L6-10 (2% each), L11-20 (1% each). Commissions are calculated and distributed daily by the smart contract \u2014 no manual tracking, no delayed payments. There's no limit on how many people you can refer at any level, and the network grows organically as each member builds their own tree.\n\n\u2705 Key Highlights:\n\u2022 L1: 12% | L2: 8% | L3: 5% | L4-5: 3% each = 31% (top 5)\n\u2022 L6-10: 2% each = 10% | L11-20: 1% each = 10% (deep 15)\n\u2022 Grand total: 51% across all 20 levels\n\u2022 Unlimited width at every level \u2014 no referral caps\n\u2022 Daily automatic commission payments by smart contract\n\n\u{1F48E} One link. 20 levels. 51% distribution. Build your empire.\n\n\u{1F310} turboloop.io",
