      original: "63_Leadership_Detail.png",
      headline: "\u{1F537} BECOME A LEADER",
      caption: "\u{1F537} BECOME A LEADER\n\u2726 The Journey From Partner to TURBO LEGEND\n\nTurboLoop's leadership journey is a clearly defined path from community participant to elite network leader. It begins when you reach 100 team members and qualify as a Partner, earning a 1% leadership bonus on your network's activity. From there, each milestone unlocks greater rewards: Senior Partner at 250 members (2%), Manager at 500 (3%), Senior Manager at 1,000 (5%), Director at 2,500 (7%), Senior Director at 5,000 (8%). At the summit stands TURBO LEGEND \u2014 requiring 10,000 team members and $1,000,000 in total team deposits \u2014 earning the maximum 10% leadership bonus. This isn't just about the percentages. Each rank represents a growing community, a widening influence, and a deepening commitment to the TurboLoop ecosystem. The summit is real. The path is clear.\n\n\u2705 Key Highlights:\n\u2022 Partner: 100 members, 1% \u2192 Senior Partner: 250, 2%\n\u2022 Manager: 500, 3% \u2192 Senior Manager: 1,000, 5%\n\u2022 Director: 2,500, 7% \u2192 Senior Director: 5,000, 8%\n\u2022 TURBO LEGEND: 10,000 members + $1M team deposit \u2192 10%\n\u2022 Each rank = greater rewards, wider influence, deeper commitment\n\n\u{1F48E} The summit awaits. Start climbing. The view is worth it.\n\n\u{1F310} turboloop.io",
